Notes: SP wins fourth straight Pointer Tipoff Tournament, beating LU in tourney for
third straight year...LU took 41-40 lead with 13:13 left and SP scored next
10 points over three-minute span...LU went from 10:01 to 2:31 of second half
without a field goal...SP's Nechuta named MVP for second straight year.
